<plot>Stan Larkin lives in a black-and-white world. That is, until he meets a new coworker, Sarah, who awakens something in him. After they connect, he dreams in vivid color: a fractured take on the day's events. When his villainous boss kidnaps Sarah, it's up to Stan to do what his real-life self never could - save the day.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?159478</url></doc>
